Rajaratnam Arrest Led Hedge Fund Analyst to Destroy Insider Data

-- B y   P a t r i c i a   H u r t a d o
-- 
2011-06-14T18:36:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-14/rajaratnam-s-arrest-led-hedge-fund-analyst-to-destroy-insider-trading-data.html
A former analyst at hedge fund Barai
Capital Management LP testified today in Manhattan federal court
that after Galleon Group LLC co-founder Raj Rajaratnam was
arrested, he destroyed some files related to inside information
provided to his firm by expert networkers.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Patricia Hurtado in New York at 
 pathurtado@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David E. Rovella at 
 drovella@bloomberg.net  